headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Nightclub Discounts & Savings on Select Vehicles
content:
Turn a previous tenant's financial woes to your advantage this week courtesy of Maze Bank Foreclosures, who are offering a 25% discount on Nightclubs, Add-Ons & Renovations, as well as 40% off all Bunkers. Plus, there’s discounts on select vehicles including:

- Imponte Deluxo – 25% off
- Festival Bus – 30% off
- Pegassi Tezeract – 30% off

Check out the Rockstar Newswire for all the details.
